Round: Second Round 
* (Aug 8 & 15)


Universidad Católica     Chi  The Strongest            Bol   3-1  1-1  4-2
Vasco da Gama            Bra  Colo Colo                Chi   0-0  3-3  3-3  5-4p
Cerro Porteño            Par  Atlético Nacional        Col   0-0  0-1  0-1
Defensor Sporting        Uru  River Plate              Arg   1-2  1-2  2-4w
Pepeganga                Ven  Independiente            Arg   0-6  0-3  0-9x
Unión Huaral             Per  Emelec                   Ecu   1-0  0-2  1-2y
Barcelona                Ecu  Progreso                 Uru   2-0  2-2  4-2z
w Aug 5 and 12
x 1st Leg Aug 4
y 1st Leg Aug 9
z 2nd Leg Aug 14
bye: Olimpia


Round: Quarter-Finals 
* (Aug 22 & 29)


Olimpia                  Par  Universidad Católica     Chi   2-0  4-4  6-4
Vasco da Gama            Bra  Atlético Nacional        Col   0-0  0-1  0-1x
River Plate              Arg  Independiente            Arg   2-0  1-1  3-1
Emelec                   Ecu  Barcelona                Ecu   0-0  0-1  0-1
* x 2nd leg replay Sep 13 in Santiago after match in Medellín (won 2-0 by Atlético Nacional) had been annulled after a protest by Vasco complaining of pressure on the referee (death threats) by local druglords


Round: Semi-Finals 
* (Sep 5 & 12)


Atlético Nacional        Col  Olimpia                  Par   1-2  3-2  4-4x 1-2p
River Plate              Arg  Barcelona                Ecu   1-0  0-1  1-1  3-4p
x 1st leg played Sep 20 in Santiago de Chile due to the incident surrounding the
  quarterfinal between Atlético Nacional and Vasco da Gama; 2nd leg Sep 26


Round: Final 

* (Oct 3 & 10)
Olimpia                  Par  Barcelona                Ecu   2-0  1-1  3-1
 

